<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">递加求积法，是指在两个乘数中有一个乘数是111，计算时，可在首尾两数字之间添上两个它们的和（如果这个和大于或者等于10就往上进一位），所得的数就是要求的积。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">52×111=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 52×111</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=5772</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>